19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:04): I used to know the capital city of every country except the ones around Russia
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:05): I haven't really needed to use it, so I'm not as good at it as I used to be.
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:06): And sometimes I know something but can't remember it when I want to use it.
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:07): My mom says it comes from trying to remember too much stuff.
00b3cc47298af9844d91e58054f5f99d (02:07): its hard to study in Malaysia btw
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:09): For me, it's always been harder to learn something new if I didn't find it interesting.
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:09): Like math. I just don't care.
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:09): And I don't care about who invented what when. I hated having to memorize stuff like that.
00b3cc47298af9844d91e58054f5f99d (02:10): so many stuff to be remembered
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:10): I didn't like it in school.
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:10): I've learned a ton of historical stuff on my own, though.
19b359533d5740a13a755666252452f2 (02:11): But in school a lot of the time they seemed to want you to remember names and dates and places.
00b3cc47298af9844d91e58054f5f99d (02:11): i hate to wake up early in the mornign just to go to school
